subtitleNullable: Sales from the Retail Trade and Food Services Report from the US Census.
descriptionNullable:
### Content
Sales from the Retail Trade and Food Services Report from the US Census. This dataset only covers Department Stores, though the report covers a wide range of retail types.
According to the [data.world](https://data.world/retail/department-store-sales), it has Public Domain License.

### Acknowledgements
I'm thankful to [data.world](https://data.world/retail/department-store-sales) for sharing this dataset. I couldn't find it on [kaggle.com](https://www.kaggle.com/), so I decided to upload it here.
